STATE of North Carolina
v.
Nathaniel Lee SIMPSON. No. 220P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 5, 2006. M. Gordon Widenhouse, Chapel Hill, for Nathaniel Lee Simpson. Robert C. Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, Seth Edwards, District Attorney, for State of NC. Prior report: ___ N.C.App. ___, 627 S.E.2d 271 .

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 25th day of April 2006 by Defendant in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th day of October 2006."
